{"title":"Inside theme+MathJax","date":"2020-03-17T15:14:13.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 17, 2020","L":"03/17/2020","MM-DD":"03-17"},"link":"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax","tags":["website"],"updated":"2020-03-17T16:28:04.546Z","content":"<p>The original Inside theme can’t render the mathmatical formula written by latex code normally. So I want to add MathJax plugin to render it.</p>\n<p>Someone has developed a plugin named “hexo-filter-mathjax-ssr”. I will add it to my website.</p>\n<h1 id=\"Installation\">Installation<a href=\"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax#Installation\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-filter-mathjax-ssr --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>If your internet speed was poor, maybe you can refer to “Migration of Hexo+Github Pages” in the root.</p>\n<h1 id=\"Config\">Config<a href=\"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax#Config\"></a></h1><p>hexo/_config.yml</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">mathjax:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">  <span class=\"title\">inlineQuote</span>: ['<span class=\"title\">MATHJAX</span>-<span class=\"title\">SSR</span>-1']</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">  <span class=\"title\">blockQuote</span>: ['<span class=\"title\">MATHJAX</span>-<span class=\"title\">SSR</span>-0']</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>done!</p>\n<h3 id=\"Reference\"><em>Reference</em><a href=\"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax#Reference\"></a></h3><p><a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/post/math-jax-ssr-example#cauchys-integral-formula\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://blog.oniuo.com/post/math-jax-ssr-example#cauchys-integral-formula</a></p>\n","next":{"title":"法院判决书","link":"2020/03/15/聪明的小耗子"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax/","toc":[{"title":"Installation","id":"Installation","index":"1"},{"title":"Config","id":"Config","index":"2"}],"reward":true}